# Laravel Dusk

## When to use

- Writing browser automation tests with ChromeDriver
- Testing JavaScript-driven UIs, SPAs, or Livewire components in a real browser
- Managing ChromeDriver versions and Dusk configuration
- Setting up CI/CD pipelines for browser tests

